{"title_page": "Oklahoma City Thunder", "text_new": "{{For|the minor league American football team|Oklahoma Thunder}}\n{{short description|Professional basketball team based in Oklahoma City, Oklahoma}}\n{{Use mdy dates|date=January 2019}}\n{{Infobox basketball club\n| name = Oklahoma City Thunder\n| current = 2019\u201320 Oklahoma City Thunder season\n| logo = Oklahoma City Thunder.svg\n| imagesize = 200px\n| conference = [[Western Conference (NBA)|Western]]\n| division = [[Northwest Division (NBA)|Northwest]]\n| founded = 1967\n| history = '''[[Seattle SuperSonics]]'''<br />1967\u20132008<br />'''Oklahoma City Thunder'''<br />2008\u2013present<ref>{{cite web|title=History: Team by Team|url=https://cdn.nba.net/assets/pdfs/2018-19-NBA-Guide-10-8.pdf#page=127|work=2018-19 Official NBA Guide|publisher=NBA Properties, Inc.|date=October 8, 2018|access-date=January 29, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=NBA.com/Stats\u2013Oklahoma City Thunder seasons|url=http://stats.nba.com/team/#!/1610612760/seasons/|website=Stats.NBA.com|access-date=October 17, 2015}}</ref>\n| arena = [[Chesapeake Energy Arena]]\n| location = [[Oklahoma City|Oklahoma City, Oklahoma]]\n| colors = Thunder blue, sunset, yellow, navy blue<ref name=\"OKCThunderUnis2019\">{{cite news|last=Crall|first=Joseph|title=Thunder Unveils New Uniform in Partnership with Oklahoma City National Memorial|url=https://www.nba.com/thunder/news/release-uniforms-190723|publisher=NBA Media Ventures, LLC|website=OKCThunder.com|date=July 23, 2019|access-date=July 23, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=General Information|url=https://www.nba.com/.element/media/2.0/teamsites/thunder/Thunder%20Guide%202018_r110518.pdf#page=3|work=2018\u201319 Oklahoma City Thunder Media Guide|publisher=NBA Properties, Inc.|date=November 5, 2018|access-date=December 2, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Oklahoma City Thunder Reproduction and Usage Guideline Sheet|url=https://mediacentral.nba.com/wp-content/uploads/logos/nba/okc/Oklahoma_City_Thunder_