ound: Becky Lynch breaks out for WWE as the 2018 Wrestler of the Year|last=Silverstein|first=Adam|date=December 26, 2018|work=[[CBS Sports]]}}</ref>\n* '''International Wrestling Federation'''\n** IWF Heavyweight Championship (1 time)<ref name=\"slam\"/>\n** IWF Tag Team Champions (1 time) \u2013 with [[Perry Saturn]]\n* '''''[[Pro Wrestling Illustrated]]'''''\n** [[PWI Feud of the Year|Feud of the Year]] (2000) {{small|vs. [[Kurt Angle]]}}<ref name=\"PWI Awards\">{{cite web|url=http://www.pwi-online.com/pages/PWIawards.html|title=PWI Awards|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121172943/http://www.pwi-online.com/pages/PWIawards.html|archivedate=January 21, 2016|url-status=live|work=[[Pro Wrestling Illustrated]]|publisher=[[Kappa Publishing Group]]|accessdate=March 6, 2018}}</ref>\n** Feud of the Year (2004) {{small|vs. [[Chris Benoit]]}}<ref name=\"PWI Awards\"/>\n** Feud of the Year (2009) {{small|vs. [[Randy Orton]]}}<ref name=\"PWI Awards\"/>\n** Feud of the Year (2013) {{small|vs. [[Daniel Bryan]] \u2013 as a member of [[The Authority (professional wrestling)|The Authority]]}}<ref name=\"PWI Awards\"/>\n** [[PWI Match of the Year|Match of the Year]] (2004) {{small|vs. Chris Benoit and Shawn Michaels at [[WrestleMania XX]]}}<ref name=\"PWI Awards\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://100megsfree4.com/wiawrestling/pages/pwi/pwimoty.htm |accessdate=June 28, 2008 |title=Pro Wrestling Illustrated Award Winners Match of the Year |publisher=Wrestling Information Archive |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080616063308/http://www.100megsfree4.com/wiawrestling/pages/pwi/pwimoty.htm |archivedate=June 16, 2008 |url-status=dead  }}</ref>\n** Match of the Year (2012) {{small|vs. The Undertaker in a [[Hell in a Cell]] match at [[WrestleMania XXVIII]]}}<ref name=\"PWI Awards\"/>\n** Most Hated Wrestler of the Decade (2000\u20132009)\n** [[PWI Most Hated Wrestler of the Year|Most Hated Wrestler of the Year]] (2003\u20132005)<ref name=\"PWI Awards\"/>\n** Most Hated Wrestl